g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190918%2Fs00001%2F949a1040bd361345c601ae53f6469758.jpg&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ea1d5341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190918%2Fs00001%2F949a1040bd361345c601ae53f6469758.jpg&h=ec277e57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190918/s00001/949a1040bd361345c601ae53f6469758.jpg</a><br />\n至於 喺夢入面 我問過手足 佢係新屋嶺定831 <br />\n佢唔答我嘅原因 好可能係兩樣都唔係<br />\n佢帶我去嗰度 可能係想同我講<br />\n我夢到嘅景象 每一樣都係代表一個地方<br />\n每一個地方都有唔同嘅用途<br />\n<br />\n利申 無再被報夢 純粹9up 求集思廣益<br />\nbtw多謝特衰政府出嚟澄清 證明香園圍呢個方向係正確嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485937-20191013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485937-20191013.htm&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=90c72092\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485937-20191013.htm&h=69d3bdd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485937-20191013.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"會不會是佢兩樣都唔係<br />\n所以答唔到你？<br />\n<br />\n而整合番陳烈士嘅預計死亡日子，被帶去嘅地方就係你夢到嘅地方？？"},{"pid":"422fd7f16f3949f830f920c13bbf7909de68ea0c","tid":1651980,"uid":78412,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7cfb56ffaaa35969f567a1c70d69463cf77c9ead","tid":1651980,"uid":254330,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"講真 我真心唔相信神鬼、報夢、問米<br />\n見隔離post仲討論得好熱烈,上埋熱門,我都唔想認同果幾個巴打<br />\n<br />\n但係我相信你講嘅野,因為睇番出post日期時間同details真係準到嚇死me<br />\n可能真係有報夢都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"無錯, 我老豆未死前我都唔信